Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.43,0:01:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}（心）ブァ～カ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.69,0:01:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}（牛島田）豚！　佐治！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.95,0:01:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}く…
